{"tid":1309382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【九龍灣美食】IKEA宜家家居美食站新出D24榴槤新地　九龍灣店獨家限定！","createTime":"2019-07-12T07:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T13:16:02.000Z","uid":47091,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"00118c85587d2ae32f68ee939a9ffaaf0901a4d1","tid":1309382,"uid":47091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:27:37.000Z","msg":"KEA宜家家居美食站又有新口味雪糕推出啦！今次新出嘅係D24榴槤新地，口感幼滑，濃郁榴槤香，仲有$9就食到。不過今次只係九龍灣店獨家限定，同樣期間限定嫁，數量有限，售完即止，各位榴槤控要把握機會去食喇！<br />\n<br />\nIKEA又有新口味雪糕推出啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/event/1024/201907/20190709163943_0_ikea-icecream-durian-cover.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Fevent%2F1024%2F201907%2F20190709163943_0_ikea-icecream-durian-cover.jpg&h=570d8970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次新出嘅係D24榴槤新地，口感幼滑，濃郁榴槤香，仲有$9就食到～<br />\n同樣期間限定嫁，數量有限，售完即止。<br />\n不過今次只係九龍灣店獨家限定，各位榴槤控別錯過啦～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/memberdata/trip/original/20140205155846-076.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fmemberdata%2Ftrip%2Foriginal%2F20140205155846-076.jpg&h=c1d8dc2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://case.ntu.edu.tw/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/1122.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcase.ntu.edu.tw%2Fblog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2F1122.jpg&h=b3dc864c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.alibabanews.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/default/files/inline-images/IMG_6047.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.alibabanews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Finline-images%2FIMG_6047.JPG&h=5ab36649&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/activity/detail/114704/%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E7%81%A3%E7%BE%8E%E9%A3%9F-ikea%E5%AE%9C%E5%AE%B6%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%85%E7%BE%8E%E9%A3%9F%E7%AB%99%E6%96%B0%E5%87%BAd24%E6%A6%B4%E6%A7%A4